who   : Lord Foul the Despiser — The Wielder & The Despiser (the bound center of all ten books).
what  : the bitterness at the heart of the world — Despiser, Corruption, Fangthane. He whispers 'you are mine,' for he is Covenant's own despair given a voice: the Land's destroyer, and the dark proof of its meaning.
